### Authentication Endpoints Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. User Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### 2. User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### 3. Admin Login (use existing admin credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 4. Email Verification (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "verification-token-here"
}

### 5. Email Verification (GET - for email links)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify?token=verification-token-here

### 6. Forgot Password Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### 7. Reset Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "reset-token-here",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### 8. Google OAuth Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/google-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "google-access-token-here",
  "idToken": "google-id-token-here"
}

### 9. Facebook OAuth Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/facebook-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "facebook-access-token-here"
}

### 10. Refresh Token (placeholder)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Logout (placeholder)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE